@page "/about"

<div class="container-fluid p-0" style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #FFD194, #D1913C); min-height: 100vh; position: relative;">

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="text-center text-white py-5" style="background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);">
        <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold" style="letter-spacing: 2px;">About Us</h1>
        <p class="lead" style="max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; opacity: 0.9;">
            Bringing joy, love, and companionship to every home—one paw at a time.
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Back to Home Button -->
    <a class="btn btn-outline-light position-absolute" href="/"
       style="top: 20px; right: 20px; border-radius: 25px; font-size: 1rem; padding: 10px 20px; transition: 0.3s ease;">
        ⬅ Back to Home
    </a>

    <!-- Content Section -->
    <div class="container py-5">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-lg-10">
                <div class="card shadow-lg p-4" style="border-radius: 20px; background: #fff8e1;">

                    <p class="fs-5" style="line-height: 1.8; color: #444;">
                        At <strong>Paws & Claws</strong>, we believe pets are more than animals—they are **family members** who bring love, laughter, and unforgettable moments into our lives. Our mission is to create **meaningful connections** between pets and people, ensuring every animal finds a warm, loving home.
                    </p>

                    <p class="fs-5" style="line-height: 1.8; color: #444;">
                        <strong>🐾 Who We Are:</strong> Founded with compassion and care, **Paws & Claws** is a trusted name in pet adoption. We collaborate with **shelters, rescue groups, and ethical breeders** to connect families with their **perfect furry companions**.
                    </p>

                    <p class="fs-5" style="line-height: 1.8; color: #444;">
                        <strong>💛 Our Commitment:</strong> Beyond adoption, we are **passionate about educating pet owners**. Through workshops, adoption events, and **free resources**, we equip families with knowledge on **pet training, health, and behavior**.
                    </p>

                    <p class="fs-5" style="line-height: 1.8; color: #444;">
                        <strong>🏡 Our Vision:</strong> Every adoption is a **story of hope**. At Paws & Claws, we believe in a world where **every pet has a home, and every home has the love of a pet**.
                    </p>

                    <p class="fs-5 text-center mt-4" style="color: #444;">
                        **Join us in making a difference. Adopt. Love. Inspire.** 🐶🐱
                    </p>

                    <!-- Call to Action -->
                    <div class="text-center mt-4">
                        <a href="/pets" class="btn btn-lg btn-primary px-5 py-2" style="border-radius: 25px;">Browse Available Pets 🐾</a>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
